# LevelDB pack runtime directories — Foundry v11+ generates packs/<name>/ from
# the tracked packs/<name>.db NeDB sources (system.json declares the .db paths)
# and rewrites them on launch/compaction. Entire dirs are runtime artifacts;
# only the .db files are distribution content. (Supersedes the narrower
# LOG/CURRENT/MANIFEST patterns from handoff §0 — 2026-07-22.)
packs/*/

# Test harness dependencies
node_modules/
